    <!-- Story -->
    <section class="section section-light">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>My Story</h2>
                <p>My path has been one of deep feeling, exploration, and transformation. I began in the world of witchcraft and magick, where I learned to listen to the unseen and explore the depths of the human spirit. This opened me to meditation, energy work, and a living relationship with the metaphysical.</p>

                <p>Over time, I journeyed into altered states of consciousness and grounded those experiences with studies in holistic counselling and complementary therapies. Along the way, I wove in somatic practices, shadow work, Reiki, and my lifelong love of philosophy, music, and emotions.</p>

                <p>I believe emotions are sacred messengers—not here to harm or rule us, but to guide, teach, and sometimes initiate great change. They act as bridges between our human experience and the lives we long to embody.</p>

                <p><strong>My role is to offer a safe, compassionate space where you can meet those emotions, hear their messages, and uncover the peace and strength within them.</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="nature-divider"></div>

    <!-- Who I Work With -->
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="two-column">
                <div>
                    <h2>Who I Work With</h2>
                    <p>My personal offering is aimed towards people who have had mind-altered experiences, the more neurodivergent, and souls that feel like black sheep to society.</p>
                    
                    <p><strong>I am here for the seekers and those wanting to free their dreams.</strong></p>

                    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">I work primarily with young teenagers through to adults in their mid-30s. This is a space for those who:</p>
                    <ul style="line-height: 2.2;">
                        <li>Have navigated altered states and psychedelic experiences</li>
                        <li>Feel deeply and intensely</li>
                        <li>Never quite fit the conventional mold</li>
                        <li>Are neurodivergent or questioning their identity</li>
                        <li>Seek authentic connection and genuine support</li>
                        <li>Want to build something meaningful in the world</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #F5F2EB; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px;">
                    <h3>My Approach</h3>
                    <p><strong>You lead, I follow.</strong> This isn't directive therapy.</p>
                    
                    <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">Sessions are pure presence—intuitive listening from a place where every part of your truth might unfold. Sometimes all at once through a single breath, sometimes in silent stillness.</p>

                    <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">There are no agendas, no performance expectations. You might speak. You might cry. You might laugh gently or rage or just sit in holy silence. Whatever unfolds is welcome. It's all medicine.</p>

                    <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: #6A6A6A;">Feeling comes from within—not from the outside. My work is about bringing feeling back into the being: heart, body, mind, and spirit coherence.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="nature-divider"></div>

