    <section class="section section-light">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>This Isn't About Bypassing Pain</h2>
                <p>This isn't about bypassing pain or simply talking through it—it's about alchemizing your story into something powerful, compassionate, and deeply you.</p>

                <p>I sought solace in older people and wise spaces. Knowing how much I suffered, I don't want others to feel alone. I want people to know they don't have to feel like a burden—I offer them a safe space to speak and be heard.</p>

                <p><strong>You don't need to be fixed. You need to be met exactly as you are.</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
